     * Current Regional Earthquake Information
     * 1996 Seismic Hazard Maps
     * Geologic Radon Potential Map - Montomery and Prince Georges
       Counties, Maryland
     * The Appalachian Basin (fact sheet)
     * Research Activities
     * Map Showing Areal Extent of the Pittsburgh Coal Bed and Horizon and
       Mined Areas of the Pittsburgh Coal Bed in Pennsylvania, Ohio, West
       Virginia, and Maryland -- map (open-file report)
     * Possible Continuous-Type (Unconventional) Gas Accumulation in Lower
       Silurian "Clinton" Sands, Medina Group, and the Tuscarora Sandstone
       in the Appalachian Basin: A Progress Report of 1995 Project
       Activities (open-file report)
     * Maryland State Minerals Information
     * Mid-Atlantic Geology and Infrastructure Case Study

   NEW JERSEY
     * Geologic Features of the Sea Bottom Around a Municipal Sludge
       Dumpsite near 39N, 73W, Offshore New Jersey and New York (open-file
       report)
     * Sewage Contamination of the Deep-Sea Floor Near the 106-Mile
       Dumpsite off New Jersey (fact sheet)
     * Current Regional Earthquake Information
     * 1996 Seismic Hazard Maps
     * New Jersey State Minerals Information
     * Little Egg Inlet - Sidescan Sonar Surveys

